i18n.icons.alternative-text:
Alt text usage

No alt text is needed for decorative or purely supportive icons. However, if an icon conveys meaningful information, it must include alt text, especially for screen reader users.

Icons in the Oblique icon library include descriptive alt text, optimized for gallery use.

For other projects, adjust the alt text to reflect the icons' specific usage.
